ustainable. This initiating coverage</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/660791312/image_660791312.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743185-costamare-attractive-valuations-and-a-3-5-percent-dividend-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 10:47:00"}, {"id": "4743200", "title": "Market Leadership Is Narrow. Your Portfolio Shouldn't Be", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Forecasting\" data-id=\"1477909330\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1477909330/image_1477909330.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RichVintage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>A select few mega cap companies drove the S&amp;P 500 Index to a ba