80 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">deepblue4you/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The analysis below covers the Employment picture released on the first Friday of every month. While most of the attention goes to the Headline Report, it can be helpful to look at the details, revisions, and other reports to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160179354/image_160179354.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743195-jobs-household-survey-shows-negative-job-gains-ytd", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 10:25:00"}, {"id": "4743179", "title": "Palantir: Be Greedy When Others Are Fearful", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smiling barista holding disposable coffee cup at take out counter of cafe\" data-id=\"1219096660\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Someone said (I believe it was Buffett) to be fearful when others are greedy, and be greedy when others are fearful.</p> <p>Well, looking at the latest SA analyst ratings for Palantir Technologies Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLTR\" title=\"Palantir Technologies Inc.\">PLTR</a></span>), it appears</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1219096660/image_1219096660.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743179-palantir-be-greedy-when-others-are-fearful", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 10:17:51"}, {"id": "4743178", "title": "Why Wolfspeed's $11 Billion Design Wins Aren't Enough", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Closeup image of a circuit board featuring a prominent electrical warning symbol\" data-id=\"2180439134\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180439134/image_2180439134.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Savusia Konstantin/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Investment Thesis </span></h2> <p><span>Silicon Carbide 'SiC' is becoming a key material for high-voltage electronics, gradually replacing traditional silicon in certain applications, including electric vehicle 'EV' power trains, battery management, and utility-grade solar and wind inverters. This shift from traditional silicon to SiC creates opportunities for investors with an equity interest</span></p>", "image": "https://st